OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FMore than #900 million of new Irish
OL,7,Finvestment into the UK is part of the
OL,8,F"flourishing" ties between Ireland and
OL,9,FBritain, Sir Keir Starmer has said.
OL,11,FThe British Prime Minister announced
OL,12,Fthe funding from Irish entities as he
OL,13,Femphasised aims to deepen co-operation
OL,14,Fbetween Dublin and London.
OL,16,FSir Keir was greeted in Cork on
OL,17,FThursday by Irish Premier Micheal
OL,18,FMartin as he arrived for the second UK-
OL,19,FIreland Summit.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
