OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FThe gathering of British and Irish
OL,7,Fministers included a roundtable with
OL,8,Fbusiness leaders in the energy and
OL,9,Finfrastructure sectors on Thursday
OL,10,Fevening.
OL,12,FThe #937 million in new investment
OL,13,Ffrom companies in Ireland is expected
OL,14,Fto create around 850 jobs across
OL,15,FLondon, Doncaster, South Wales and
OL,16,FScotland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
