OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FGas Networks Ireland is to invest #170
OL,7,Fmillion; Amach, the AI and cloud-
OL,8,Fcomputing company to the aviation
OL,9,Fsector, is to invest #45 million and
OL,10,Fcreate 150 jobs; and Focus Capital
OL,11,FPartners is to invest #3 million.
OL,13,FAyrton Group, which is based in Cork,
OL,14,Fwill invest more than #1 million in
OL,15,Fits UK arm to boost "AI-empowered
OL,16,Fservices" and double its London team.
OL,26,@wD@UOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
