OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FAs the high cost of fuel and energy is
OL,7,Fexpected to dominate discussions at
OL,8,Fthe Cork summit, energy links between
OL,9,FBritain and Ireland will also be
OL,10,Femphasised.
OL,12,FAn interconnector between Wales and
OL,13,FIreland is expected to provide enough
OL,14,Fpower for 570,000 homes, and represent
OL,15,Fat least #740 million of private
OL,16,Finvestment.
OL,18,FA separate energy connector between
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland and Ireland aims to
OL,20,Flower electricity costs on the island.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FThe UK and Irish governments are also
OL,7,Fexpected to discuss joint exercises to
OL,8,Ftest the resilience of subsea fibre
OL,9,Foptic cables which run between the UK
OL,10,Fand Ireland, and a "crackdown" on
OL,11,Fshadow fleets and other threats in the
OL,12,FIrish and Celtic seas through a
OL,13,Frefreshed UK-Ireland Defence
OL,14,FMemorandum of Understanding.
OL,16,FSir Keir said: "As people on both
OL,17,Fsides of the Irish Sea are feeling the
OL,18,Fcost-of-living squeeze, we are
OL,19,Finvesting in partnerships that make us
OL,20,Fbetter off and more secure.
OL,26,@rD@TOUrD@^O]xD@POU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,F"The UK's close friendship with
OL,7,FIreland is going from strength to
OL,8,Fstrength and I am pleased that we are
OL,9,Fgoing further in working together on
OL,10,Fgrowth, energy, security and more.
OL,12,F"This new Irish investment coming into
OL,13,Fthe UK is one part of a much bigger
OL,14,Fpicture of our flourishing cultural,
OL,15,Fcommercial and security ties.
OL,17,F"The action this Government has taken
OL,18,Fto reset relationships and deepen
OL,19,Fpartnerships with our closest allies
OL,20,Fis paying off.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,F"It will help us withstand global
OL,7,Fchallenges and protect money in the
OL,8,Fpockets of families up and down the
OL,9,Fcountry."
OL,11,FRobert Adams, president of Focus
OL,12,FCapital Partners, said the UK was "a
OL,13,Fhighly attractive market for
OL,14,Finvestment".
OL,16,FHe added: "Expanding our presence in
OL,17,FLondon allows us to work more closely
OL,18,Fwith ambitious UK companies and to
OL,19,Fsupport Irish and international
OL,20,Fbusinesses and investors seeking
OL,21,Fopportunities in the UK market."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]tD@cOUvD@KO]xD@KOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
