PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FAyrton managing director Kieran
OL,7,FLinehan said its strategy for several
OL,8,Fyears had been to expand beyond
OL,9,FIreland.
OL,11,F"Thus, the UK market has always been
OL,12,Four most strategic fit, for many
OL,13,Freasons," he said.
OL,15,F"These include the UK being a
OL,16,Fsignificantly larger market than
OL,17,FIreland, it is a very diverse and
OL,18,Festablished market, with whom we have
OL,19,Fan extremely strong relationship,
OL,20,Fculturally.
OL,26,@sD@AOUuD@IO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
