PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,F"Doing business in the UK for Irish
OL,7,Fcompanies is much easier than other
OL,8,Fmarkets, due to the historical
OL,9,Frelationships, geographical location,
OL,10,Four common language and cultural
OL,11,Fsynergies.
OL,13,F"Additionally, investing in the UK
OL,14,Fmarket is an opportunity to enhance
OL,15,Fthe services we provide, including
OL,16,Fengineering and associated services,
OL,17,Fto our clients and we have always
OL,18,Fwanted to bring our Irish market
OL,19,Fexpertise to compete in such a larger
OL,20,Fmarket that is the UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,F"With our 'Group' structure, we feel
OL,7,Fwe can cost-effectively serve the UK
OL,8,Fmarket and our UK clients, thus
OL,9,Finvestment in the UK is a good return
OL,10,Fon our investment in that market."
OL,12,FO'Flynn Group chairman and chief
OL,13,Fexecutive Michael O'Flynn said it
OL,14,Fwould deliver student accommodation
OL,15,Fvalued at #35 million in Manchester.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
