PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773421881
OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,FHe added: "The UK remains one of the
OL,7,Fmost important and dynamic student
OL,8,Faccommodation markets globally, and
OL,9,Four new Manchester development
OL,10,Freflects our continued confidence in
OL,11,FUK university cities and our long-term
OL,12,Fcommitment to delivering high-quality,
OL,13,Fprofessionally managed accommodation
OL,14,Fthat supports students, universities,
OL,15,Fand local communities.
OL,26,@nD@KOU
