OL,3,CNew Irish investment into UK part of
OL,4,C'flourishing' ties, Keir Starmer says
OL,6,F"We have built a strong operational
OL,7,Fplatform in the UK over nearly three
OL,8,Fdecades, and we continue to see
OL,9,Fattractive opportunities to invest
OL,10,Ffurther in partnership with
OL,11,Finstitutional capital."
